CaptionCapture
==============

Detect and recognize onscreen text in news broadcast videos.

License: MIT

Requirements:
-------------
1.) OpenCV 2.4, scons, python-dev
2.) https://github.com/virtuald/python-tesseract-sip

Building:
---------
1.) Install requirements, python-tesseract-sip 
2.) Run scons in source directory

Example:
--------
python segment.py video_file.avi